data.description: This well maintained property has been very loved and cared for and is ready for its new owner! Provides 4 beds, 3 baths, 2 very expansive living areas, nice sized bedrooms and an eat-in kitchen. Newer paint and carpet, and added insulation in the attic. Come make this one your own! Some furniture may be negotiable. Seller is motivated, all offers will be considered!
